=Role: You are a content rewriting specialist. Minimal changes, just reformat for social reposting.

Context:
- Keyword: {{ $json.Keyword }}
- Landing Page: {{ $json['Landing Page'] }}
- Title: {{ $json.Title }}
- Content: {{ $json.Content }}
- Critical Instructions: {{ $json['Critical Instructions'] }}

Goal: Create an informational social sharing post with headline that adds value.

Rules:
- Headline: 6-8 words, informational, no special chars like "*"
- Content: plain text, paragraphs of max 50 words, no intro/conclusion, no links
- First 250 chars (including headline) must stand alone as a Twitter-ready summary
- Image prompt: realistic, professional, business-appropriate. NO brand logos, NO cyberpunk themes, NO brand references
- Paragraphs must use real line breaks (\n\n between paragraphs)

Do not invent information. Intent must match the source.

parameters.jsCode:
// Combine AI output + image + row data into one clean object
const imgResponse = $input.first().json;
const imageUrl = imgResponse?.data?.[0]?.url || '';

const ai = $('4. AI Agent — Generate Post Content').first().json.output;
const row = $('3. Split — Loop Over Each Row').item.json;

const headline = ai.Headline || '';
const content = ai.Content || '';
const landingPage = row['Landing Page'] || '';
const domainId = row['Domain ID'] || '';

const postText = `${headline}\n\n${content}\nRead more: ${landingPage}`;

return [{
  json: { headline, content, landingPage, domainId, imageUrl, postText }
}];
